info.name: UPS Shipping
info.description:
Prepare your package for shipment, manage returns, and cancel scheduled shipments.

Visit the full [UPS Shipping Documentation](https://developer.ups.com/api/reference?loc=en_US#tag/Shipping_other) for more details!

request.description: This HTTP POST request takes in origin information (**ShipFrom**), destination information (**ShipTo**), **PaymentInformation**, and **Package** information and returns the cost of the movement as well as a UPS 1Z tracking number that represents the movement.
